1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Walong Daan=

2
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:58,540
Lolo, Lola.

3
00:01:58,540 --> 00:02:00,030
(Taon 1993)

4
00:02:00,030 --> 00:02:00,880
Songge.

5
00:02:00,890 --> 00:02:03,210
Mangyaring kumpirmahin kung mananatili ang mga ito
mga miyembro ng iyong pamilya,

6
00:02:03,210 --> 00:02:04,130
Gao Peiliang

7
00:02:04,130 --> 00:02:05,260
at Liu Xiwen?

8
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:08,170
Nang umalis sila kaninang umaga,

9
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:09,850
maayos naman sila.

10
00:02:09,850 --> 00:02:11,500
Hindi pwede.

11
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:12,340
Tama na, anak.

12
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:13,690
Mr. Chen,

13
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:16,380
sabihin mo sa akin kung bakit nangyari ito.

14
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:17,290
Songge,

15
00:02:17,290 --> 00:02:18,780
dahil sa ulan,

16
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:21,010
bato mula sa pagguho ng lupa

17
00:02:21,010 --> 00:02:23,010
saktan ang kotse ng lolo't lola mo.

18
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:24,260
Dahil sa labis na pagkawala ng dugo,

19
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,500
hindi sila nailigtas ng ospital.

20
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:27,380
Kontrolin ang iyong sarili.

21
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:30,260
Songge, magpakabait ka.

22
00:02:30,290 --> 00:02:32,170
- Songge.
- Songge.

23
00:02:32,170 --> 00:02:33,410
- Songge.
- Huwag kang malungkot.

24
00:02:33,410 --> 00:02:34,450
Okay lang, Songge.

25
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:37,980
Para kang anak sa amin.

26
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,850
Aalagaan ka naming mabuti.

27
00:02:44,850 --> 00:02:46,730
- Songge.
- Songge.

28
00:02:47,730 --> 00:02:49,170
Lumabas na ang resulta ng blood test.

29
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:50,500
(Ulat sa Lab ng Ospital ng mga Manggagawa ng Fengyang Mine)
Ang serum creatinine ay nasa 1,200 na.

30
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:52,060
Ano ang ibig sabihin nito?

31
00:02:52,820 --> 00:02:54,060
Ito ay uremia.

32
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:54,940
Kailangan niya ng dialysis.

33
00:02:57,540 --> 00:02:59,450
Paano kaya ang Songge

34
00:02:59,450 --> 00:03:00,660
sobrang nakakaawa?

35
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:02,170
No family since she was little,

36
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:04,730
at ngayon, mayroon siyang sakit na ito.

37
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:07,100
Ang sakit na ito ay ang pinaka-draining.

38
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:08,100
Pag-draining para sa pasyente,

39
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:09,980
draining para sa pamilya.

40
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:11,340
Kung magkamali,

41
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:12,890
maaaring masira ang buong pamilya.

42
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:14,980
Alam mo ba

43
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:17,500
magkano ang isang dialysis session?

44
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:19,110
Kailangan natin siyang gamutin
hindi alintana ang gastos.

45
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:34,820
=Episode 12=
(Lumang Coal Washing Plant)

46
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:46,050
Hui.

47
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:48,810
Hui!

48
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:23,020
(Public Security)

49
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:23,860
Lumabas ka ng sasakyan.

50
00:05:27,850 --> 00:05:28,690
Direk Chen.

51
00:05:30,930 --> 00:05:31,770
Nasaan ang tao?

52
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:33,660
Tumakbo siya.

53
00:06:10,850 --> 00:06:12,900
Mama, ano pa ang ginagawa mo dito?

54
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:17,850
Anong klaseng kaarawan ito?

55
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:19,300
Nay, pasensya na po.

56
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:23,460
Bigla kong napagtanto na nakalimutan ko ang mga kandila,
kaya naisipan kong lumabas para bumili.

57
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:25,490
Ngunit tinakbo ko ang buong Fengyang
at wala akong mahanap.

58
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:30,180
Ano ito?

59
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,020
Hindi ko pala nakalimutan.

60
00:06:35,610 --> 00:06:36,450
Nanay,

61
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:37,420
nasaan si Dad?

62
00:06:38,810 --> 00:06:40,250
Same as you, acting crazy.

63
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:46,740
Nanay.

64
00:07:13,130 --> 00:07:14,050
Sige, Nanay.

65
00:07:14,050 --> 00:07:15,930
Huwag ka nang magalit, okay?

66
00:07:15,930 --> 00:07:17,250
Maging masaya ka.

67
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:21,110
Kailangan nating hipan ang mga kandila
para mabilang ito bilang kaarawan.

68
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:29,620
Hui, bumalik ka.

69
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:31,540
Tatay.

70
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:34,810
May dumating
sa bahay ni Director Tong,

71
00:07:35,410 --> 00:07:36,660
kaya pina-cover niya ako sa shift niya.

72
00:07:37,850 --> 00:07:39,730
Maraming nangyayari
sa istasyon ngayon,

73
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:41,540
at kulang tayo sa tauhan,

74
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:42,780
kaya ayun late na ako nakabalik.

75
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:45,010
Huwag kang magalit.

76
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:46,620
Happy Birthday.

77
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:50,500
galit ka ba

78
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:52,980
Nanay,

79
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:54,580
since nandito na si Dad,

80
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,580
magsindi tayo ng kandila.

81
00:08:09,170 --> 00:08:11,250
Dad, pwede mo bang patayin ang ilaw?

82
00:08:12,220 --> 00:08:13,060
Tama.

83
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:14,860
Patayin ang ilaw.

84
00:08:16,810 --> 00:08:18,050
Patayin ang ilaw.

85
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:28,540
Ni-page mo lang ako.

86
00:08:35,650 --> 00:08:36,730
kahit ano?

87
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:49,130
Ano ang problema?

88
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,530
Tinatanong ko kung paged mo ako

89
00:08:51,530 --> 00:08:53,010
ngayon lang.

90
00:08:53,010 --> 00:08:53,850
Ayos ba ang lahat?

91
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:00,770
Tinatanong ko lang kung nakabalik ka na.

92
00:09:11,370 --> 00:09:12,210
Nanay,

93
00:09:12,530 --> 00:09:13,370
gumawa ng isang kahilingan.

94
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:16,820
Halika na.

95
00:09:18,730 --> 00:09:20,420
Ano kayang wish ko?

96
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:21,530
Sana lang

97
00:09:21,530 --> 00:09:23,530
na ang aming pamilya

98
00:09:23,530 --> 00:09:24,850
maaaring manatiling masaya at maayos.

99
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:29,370
Nanay, ang aming pamilya
ay tiyak na masaya at maayos.

100
00:09:30,850 --> 00:09:34,010
- Maligayang kaarawan sa iyo.
- Maligayang kaarawan sa iyo.

101
00:09:34,850 --> 00:09:41,610
- Maligayang kaarawan sa iyo.
- Maligayang kaarawan sa iyo.

102
00:09:41,610 --> 00:09:44,940
- Sana hindi ka na lang magagalit.
- Sana hindi ka na lang magagalit.

103
00:09:46,490 --> 00:09:47,330
Halika na.

104
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:49,880
Okay.

105
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:51,130
Maligayang Kaarawan,

106
00:09:51,130 --> 00:09:51,970
Nanay!

107
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:54,900
Napakaganda nito.

108
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,490
Nanay, ang kutsilyo.

109
00:09:59,850 --> 00:10:01,180
Sige, putulin ko na.

110
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:05,940
(Maligayang Kaarawan, Nanay)

111
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,340
- Gamitin ang isang ito.
- Sige.

112
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:10,610
Ibigay mo muna kay Hui.

113
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:11,460
Ngayon, para sa iyong ama.

114
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:13,180
Dad, mauna na po kayo.

115
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:14,780
salamat po.

116
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,350
Tatay.

117
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:19,420
Hui, narito ang isang malaking piraso para sa iyo.

118
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:20,260
Salamat, Nanay.

119
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:23,660
Happy Birthday.

120
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:28,300
Napakalambot ng cake na ito.

121
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:29,420
Ang sarap.

122
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:30,820
Tatay,

123
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:33,180
Espesyal na binili ni Songge ang cake na ito.

124
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:34,820
Ito ay walang asukal, kaya maaari kang kumain ng higit pa.

125
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:38,890
Napaka thoughtful ni Songge.

126
00:10:45,490 --> 00:10:47,180
Hui, oras na.

127
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,180
Malayo pa ang lalakbayin mo.

128
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:49,130
Dapat kang bumalik ngayon.

129
00:10:49,130 --> 00:10:50,490
Ayos lang, Mom.
Birthday mo ngayon.

130
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:51,710
Mananatili ako sa iyo ng kaunti pa.

131
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:54,050
Kumain na kami ng cake,
at nagawa ko na ang wish.

132
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,530
Okay lang, next time na lang ulit.

133
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:57,010
Ang pangunahing bagay
ay na ang biyahe ay masyadong mahaba.

134
00:10:58,850 --> 00:10:59,690
Sige, kung ganoon.

135
00:11:00,610 --> 00:11:02,090
Mom, Dad, babalik ako.

136
00:11:02,610 --> 00:11:03,460
- Okay.
- Okay.

137
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:06,180
Dahan dahan lang sa daan.

138
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:07,020
Hui,

139
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:09,940
pwede ba akong sumakay sayo?

140
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:15,010
Saan ka pupunta ngayon?

141
00:11:15,010 --> 00:11:16,420
Nasa istasyon pa rin si Direk Tong.

142
00:11:16,420 --> 00:11:18,300
Kailangan kong pumunta at kunin ang kanyang shift.

143
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,580
Ilang hakbang na lang.

144
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:21,100
Bakit mo pinapa-drive si Hui?

145
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:22,370
Tinatamad lang akong maglakad.

146
00:11:22,370 --> 00:11:24,010
Ano bang masama kung ipagmaneho ako ng anak ko?

147
00:11:24,010 --> 00:11:24,850
Okay lang ba yun?

148
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,260
Syempre, ayos lang.

149
00:11:55,940 --> 00:11:56,780
Sige.

150
00:12:04,130 --> 00:12:04,970
Hui,

151
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:06,580
pumasok ka na rin sa loob.

152
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:08,100
Tatay, gabi na.

153
00:12:08,100 --> 00:12:09,310
Kailangan ko pang bumalik sa lungsod.

154
00:12:11,010 --> 00:12:12,770
Pumasok ka na lang.

155
00:12:12,770 --> 00:12:13,610
Tungkol saan ito?

156
00:12:14,130 --> 00:12:15,340
Malalaman mo kapag nasa loob ka na.

157
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:38,540
Tatay,

158
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:40,610
bakit mo ako pinapasok?

159
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,370
Dad, anong ginagawa mo?

160
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,060
Bakit mo ako ikinukulong?

161
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:51,530
Tatay, bakit?

162
00:12:51,530 --> 00:12:52,620
Bakit mo ako ikinukulong?

163
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,340
Hindi mo alam kung bakit?

164
00:12:55,770 --> 00:12:57,370
Ano ang dapat kong malaman?

165
00:12:57,370 --> 00:12:58,490
Hiniling mo sa akin na sumakay,
at dinala kita dito,

166
00:12:58,490 --> 00:12:59,610
tapos kinulong mo ako.

167
00:12:59,610 --> 00:13:00,730
Kailangan mong sabihin sa akin kung bakit.

168
00:13:00,730 --> 00:13:01,600
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin dito?

169
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:02,770
Tumigil ka sa paglalaro sa akin!

170
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:04,850
Alam mo nang eksakto

171
00:13:04,850 --> 00:13:05,730
ang ginawa mo!

172
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:18,580
(24-Oras na Serbisyo. Bayan ng Fengyang
Police Station, Jiangbin Municipal PSB)

173
00:13:18,580 --> 00:13:21,260
(Pampublikong Seguridad ng Tao)

174
00:13:27,130 --> 00:13:27,970
Direktor Tong,

175
00:13:28,580 --> 00:13:29,420
paano ito?

176
00:13:32,490 --> 00:13:33,580
Nagsasabing walang alam.

177
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:35,540
Direktor Tong,

178
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,700
nasaan ang ating mga lalaki na nakabantay?

179
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:39,610
Nang makarating ako sa coal washing pool,
ito ay itim na itim,

180
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:41,700
at hindi ko nakita
isa sa ating mga tao.

181
00:13:41,700 --> 00:13:42,650
Nagkaroon ng emergency.

182
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:45,260
Isang home invasion robbery
naganap sa kanluran ng bayan.

183
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:47,300
Ang istasyon ay shorthanded,

184
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,420
kaya pina-deploy ko lahat doon.

185
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,610
Gusto kong sabihin sa iyo

186
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:52,100
nung kausap namin kanina,

187
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:53,580
pero masama ang signal mo.

188
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:54,850
Pagkatapos, naka-off ang iyong telepono.

189
00:13:54,850 --> 00:13:56,420
Hindi ako makalusot sayo.

190
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:58,420
Direktor Tong,

191
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:00,350
mayroon bang anumang bagay sa bayang ito
mas mahalaga

192
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:01,610
kaysa sa cough syrup case?

193
00:14:02,730 --> 00:14:04,300
Huwag masyadong mabalisa.

194
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:05,420
Tungkol sa kaso ni Hui,

195
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:07,340
kailangan nating suriin muli ang sitwasyon.

196
00:14:07,340 --> 00:14:09,100
Kailangan nating magbago
ang paraan ng interogasyon.

197
00:14:09,100 --> 00:14:10,100
Gayundin,

198
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:12,300
ang desisyon ng Bureau sa iyong pagtanggi

199
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:13,300
pumasok na.

200
00:14:14,340 --> 00:14:16,940
Habang si Hui ay suspek sa kaso,

201
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:18,730
bilang isang direktang kamag-anak,

202
00:14:18,730 --> 00:14:20,130
kailangan mong itigil ang iyong sarili.

203
00:14:20,130 --> 00:14:21,100
susundin ko.

204
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,060
Umuwi ka na.

205
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:24,580
Hindi alintana kung ginawa ito ni Hui o hindi,

206
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:26,490
kayo ay mag-ama.

207
00:14:26,490 --> 00:14:28,060
Ang mga bagay ay naging
masyadong tense sa pagitan niyo,

208
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,820
so how will you face each other later?

209
00:14:30,610 --> 00:14:31,450
Direktor Tong,

210
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:32,950
lahat ng ginagawa ko

211
00:14:32,970 --> 00:14:34,610
ay upang iligtas siya, hindi ba?

212
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:36,180
Sinong mag-aakalang matatapos siya

213
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:38,060
bilang pangunahing suspek?

214
00:14:38,060 --> 00:14:39,010
Kung hindi niya maintindihan

215
00:14:39,010 --> 00:14:40,010
bakit ko ginagawa ito,

216
00:14:41,770 --> 00:14:42,980
tapos ang tanga niya.

217
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:44,100
Ang pangunahing isyu ngayon

218
00:14:44,100 --> 00:14:45,890
ay wala kang anumang ebidensya

219
00:14:45,890 --> 00:14:48,460
nagpapatunay na ito ay talagang Hui.

220
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:49,530
Pagpapanatili sa kanya sa kustodiya

221
00:14:49,530 --> 00:14:50,610
batay sa hinala lamang

222
00:14:50,610 --> 00:14:52,180
ay labag sa mga patakaran.

223
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:53,530
Nang walang direktang ebidensya,

224
00:14:54,370 --> 00:14:56,010
kapag lumipas na ang 24 na oras,

225
00:14:56,010 --> 00:14:57,940
kailangan mong palayain siya.

226
00:15:07,420 --> 00:15:08,460
Direktang ebidensya...

227
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,980
Siguro meron talaga ako.

228
00:15:20,650 --> 00:15:21,490
Well?

229
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:23,250
Pwede na ba ako?

230
00:15:23,250 --> 00:15:24,220
Chen Hui,

231
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:25,340
hubarin mo ang iyong damit.

232
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:26,220
Anong ibig mong sabihin?

233
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:29,370
Nasabi ko na lahat ng kailangan kong sabihin.

234
00:15:29,370 --> 00:15:30,460
Bakit ako maghuhubad?

235
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:32,100
Gawin mo lang ang sinabi sa iyo.

236
00:15:32,100 --> 00:15:33,610
Nakipagtulungan ako sa lahat.

237
00:15:33,610 --> 00:15:35,420
Hindi mo maaaring paulit-ulit na gawin ito.

238
00:15:35,420 --> 00:15:36,980
Ito ay istasyon ng pulisya.

239
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:38,890
Inaasahan namin na kayo ay makikipagtulungan.

240
00:15:38,890 --> 00:15:40,130
Alisin ang mga ito.

241
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:40,980
Halika na.

242
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:41,940
Tulungan mo siya.

243
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:43,300
Mangyaring makipagtulungan sa amin.

244
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:46,020
Ako mismo ang gagawa.

245
00:15:56,740 --> 00:15:58,700
(Holding Room)

246
00:16:03,530 --> 00:16:05,130
Direk Tong, kumusta na?

247
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:05,970
yun lang.

248
00:16:06,170 --> 00:16:07,210
Hintayin natin ang resulta.

249
00:16:07,850 --> 00:16:08,690
Tara na.

250
00:16:27,340 --> 00:16:28,180
Malaking lalaki,

251
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:31,010
ingat sa daan.

252
00:16:31,010 --> 00:16:32,180
Tumawag na ako

253
00:16:32,180 --> 00:16:33,650
Liu Na at Kang Limin.

254
00:16:33,650 --> 00:16:35,690
Pagdating mo sa municipal PSB,
makikipag-coordinate sila sa iyo.

255
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:36,590
- Okay.
- Ayos.

256
00:16:42,490 --> 00:16:43,940
Gabi na kasi. Sino ang tumatawag?

257
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:48,130
Malamang Songge.

258
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:50,420
Hongbing, sagutin mo.

259
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:52,250
Hanggang sa lumabas ang mga resulta,

260
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:53,610
