289
00:17:50,010 --> 00:17:51,330
Para maghanap ng damit para kay Chen Hui.

290
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:52,770
Nagyeyelo na.

291
00:17:52,770 --> 00:17:53,900
Hindi natin siya hahayaang magkasakit.

292
00:17:59,330 --> 00:18:00,170
