430
00:28:50,330 --> 00:28:52,860
Ngayon ko lang naramdaman
na si Hui ay nasa napakasamang kalooban.

431
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:55,050
May magandang pagkakataon

432
00:28:55,050 --> 00:28:56,720
uuwi na siya
para magreklamo sa kanyang ina.

433
00:29:10,250 --> 00:29:11,090
Lolo.

434
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:12,860
Hui, bumalik ka.

435
00:29:13,530 --> 00:29:14,530
Dumating ako para makita ka.

436
00:29:16,090 --> 00:29:16,930
Lolo,

437
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:18,420
